# Optional. Server-side API keys used by /api/generate when a user hasn't
# provided their own key in Settings (BYOK). Set the one(s) matching the
# provider(s) you want available. Without any key (server or BYOK), everything
# works except AI card generation.
#
# Anthropic (Claude) — https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# OpenAI — https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=
